module works fine and quake3 works great, but when I compile the kernel
as smp (I have a dual proccessor p2-300 computer), and recompile NVIDIA
KERNEL, the modules load, but X dumps out saying it lost the connection
to X server. Additionally, it creates this Oops in my system log
